description: France reports 833 fatalities in the past 24 hours, the highest since its coronavirus outbreak began.
title: Coronavirus: France records highest daily death toll of 833
title_page: Coronavirus: France records highest daily death toll of 833 - BBC News
maintext: "This will probably be a bit like walking the tightrope. If we stand still along the way we could fall and if we go too fast it can go wrong. Therefore, we must take one cautious step at a time," she told a briefing.
